      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Make the sponge",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Preheat the oven to 180°C fan. Butter and line two round tins. Beat the {{unsalted-butter}} for the sponge with the {{caster-sugar}} until very pale and fluffy, at least 4 minutes. Beat in the {{eggs}} one at a time. Fold in the sifted {{plain-flour}}, {{baking-powder}}, and {{sea-salt-fine}}. Stir in the dissolved {{coffee-instant}} for the sponge, then fold in the {{walnuts}} for the sponge. Divide evenly between the two tins. Bake for 25 to 28 minutes until a skewer comes out clean and the sponges are pulling away from the edges.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Make the coffee buttercream",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Beat the {{unsalted-butter}} for the buttercream until pale. Add the sifted {{icing-sugar}} in three batches, beating between each addition. Beat in the dissolved {{coffee-instant}} for the buttercream until smooth and glossy. This is the ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "coffee buttercream",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmp9yg3b90000rsv474gzotu8"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": ": it should taste distinctly of coffee.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Assemble",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Cool the sponges completely. Sandwich with one third of the buttercream. Spread the remaining buttercream over the top and sides. Press the walnut halves around the top edge to decorate.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
